     LEFT JOIN VIEWpagosPRCMA d ON a.numfactu = d.numfactu  
       WHERE
       a.fechafac ='1/3/2020' AND   a.cod_subgrupo = 'CONSULTA' and  a.statfact=3  and d.desTipoTargeta is  not null and a.usuario='drivera' 
       GROUP BY  
       desTipoTargeta  
       Order by 
       desTipoTargeta

            where con.fechafac between '2019-12-30' and '01/03/2020' and statfact <>'2' group by con.fechafac  ORDER BY con.fechafac
